103
00:09:16,700 --> 00:09:18,000
<i> Yeah...</i>

104
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:22,467
<i>Papa really made it hard
this year.</i>

105
00:09:22,467 --> 00:09:24,500
<i>Probably,
it's somewhere in the hotel.</i>

106
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:28,100
