125
00:10:09,167 --> 00:10:10,833
<i> You still haven't found it?</i>

126
00:10:10,833 --> 00:10:13,167
<i>Come on, you guys.
Just be patient.</i>

127
00:10:13,167 --> 00:10:14,600
<i> You'll find it eventually.</i>

128
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,333
<i>Just give us a clue, Pa,
please!</i>

129
00:10:16,333 --> 00:10:17,800
<i>- Yeah, Pa.
- Please, Pa.</i>

130
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:20,300
