you'll be the ones deciding</i>

157
00:11:32,267 --> 00:11:33,667
<i> what to do with your lives.</i>

158
00:11:35,533 --> 00:11:38,400
<i>But I only have
one request.</i>

159
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:39,767
<i> What is it, Papa?</i>

160
00:11:42,767 --> 00:11:43,800
<i> I hope...</i>

161
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:47,933
<i>you'll love each other
as brothers, okay?</i>

162
00:11:47,933 --> 00:11:50,267
