love each other,</i>

163
00:11:50,267 --> 00:11:53,367
<i>even if you have
different moms.</i>

164
00:11:53,367 --> 00:11:54,467
Hmm?

165
00:11:54,467 --> 00:11:56,733
<i> Look out for each other...</i>

166
00:11:56,733 --> 00:11:59,200
<i> Take care of each other.</i>

167
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:03,333
<i>- Do you promise?
- I promise, Papa.</i>

168
00:12:03,333 --> 00:12:04,800
<i> I promise.</i>

169
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,533
<i> I promise.</i>

170
00:12:06,533 --> 00:12:08,600
