178
00:12:44,667 --> 00:12:47,667
[YOUNG JADE]<i> Kiko! Have you
</i> found the Easter Egg yet?

179
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:48,633
<i> Not yet.</i>

180
00:12:52,733 --> 00:12:53,867
<i>- Come on
- Come on!</i>

181
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,733
