on the other island?</i>

197
00:13:39,300 --> 00:13:42,400
<i>Well, I'm still thinking
about it.</i>

198
00:13:43,633 --> 00:13:46,433
[FEDERICO]<i> But if you become
</i> my business partner,

199
00:13:46,433 --> 00:13:47,533
