208
00:14:13,467 --> 00:14:15,467
<i> Kiko, let's go back.</i>

209
00:14:15,467 --> 00:14:17,700
<i> The Golden Egg might be there.</i>

210
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:19,333
<i> Come with me.</i>

211
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,967
[UNEASY MUSIC PLAYING]

212
00:14:25,967 --> 00:14:30,433
[YOUNG JADE]
<i> What are we doing here?</i>

213
00:14:30,467 --> 00:14:32,833
[YOUNG KIKO]
<i> The Easter Egg might be here.</i>

214
00:14:46,067 --> 00:14:49,733
<i> Kiko, come on already!</i>

215
00:14:49,733 --> 00:14:52,133
<i>Shh...
I'm looking for something.</i>

216
00:14:52,133 --> 00:14:53,867
<i> Just follow me.</i>

217
00:14:55,067 --> 00:14:58,600
<i>I don't think the Golden Egg
is here.</i>

218
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:00,533
<i> Come on!</i>

219
00:15:00,533 --> 00:15:03,367
<i>Don't be scared.
There's two of us.</i>

220
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:06,533
<i> Just look around.</i>

221
00:15:06,533 --> 00:15:08,100
- [MOUSE SQUEAKS]
- [CAN CLANGING]

222
00:15:08,100 --> 00:15:11,800
- [SCREAMS]
- [OBJECTS SHATTER]

223
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:13,633
<i> Jade! That was just a rat!</i>

224
00:15:17,833 --> 00:15:18,833
